      "id": "2034983457906942134",
      "text": "This is a perfect example of AI doing something actually useful instead of generating generic content nobody asked for. Taking YOUR sources and transforming them into watchable summaries solves the real problem: people capture information all day but never revisit it. Switching the output format from text to video lowers the friction of retrieval dramatically.",
